               <h3> Laws in India applicable to an NGO</h3>
                NGOs can be registered in India under any of the following laws:
                <br>
                a. Trust under Indian Trusts Act, 1882 <br>
                b. Society under Societies Registration Act 1860 <br>
                c. Section 8 Company under Companies Act, 2013 <br>
        </p>
        
